      DESC="mtr (matt's traceroute) is a combination of traceroute and ping.

mtr (matt's traceroute) is a system administrators utility 
to trace the route ip packets from the current system take 
in getting to some destination system.
Superior to traceroute it also shows the 
times packages take from that points like ping.
